Subject: Change server ip on installed client
Description: I configured the Server IP incorrectly during deployment in Intune, but the client has already been installed. Is there a way to change the Server IP without reinstalling?
What_We_Know__c: The customer asked for the change IP scripts
Next_Steps__c: The scripts were provided - waiting for the customer to confirm.
Solution_Comment__c: The change IP script worked and the EPP Clients are now communicating with the EPP Server.
